{"tid":2014260,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"西班牙外相：中國產品的質量始終抱有信心、支持世衛組織繼續在全球抗疫合作中發揮應有作用","createTime":"2020-05-13T02:13:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T07:59:07.000Z","uid":23707,"like":3,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fde53d5635427508c12fd0beb2c6b42c258cd49e","tid":2014260,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T02:13:57.000Z","msg":"國務委員兼外長王毅與西班牙外相岡薩雷斯通電話。<br />\n<br />\n王毅指出，近來，個別國家政客為推卸自身抗疫不力的責任，把疫情政治化，病毒標籤化，攻擊抹黑中國，這種做法無助本國疫情防控，也不利全球抗疫努力，相信西班牙能夠堅持客觀公正立場，推動國際抗疫合作，特別是支持世衛組織繼續在全球抗疫鬥爭中發揮領導和協調作用。<br />\n<br />\n岡薩雷斯表示，西班牙對中國產品的質量始終抱有信心並在華採購大量抗疫物資，又說西班牙支持世衛組織繼續在全球抗疫合作中發揮應有作用，希望歐中加快推進雙邊投資協定談判，深化經貿合作，在共同抗疫過程中不斷加強歐中關係。"},{"pid":"84bcea5e523cd42160f7bfd7d3d941083bb6ca88","tid":2014260,"uid":84081,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T02:15:18.000Z","msg":"拉莫斯中毒不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"421e4768eae90d73313019315fca049edfe31c34","tid":2014260,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T02:17:48.000Z","msg":"傻西"},{"pid":"86f8eb4b9e2cfb2965b4b855c886f2381561907e","tid":2014260,"uid":315761,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T02:21:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />條路自己揀 仆街唔好喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed238c77f86325eb7044d104bd4254011f0742a3","tid":2014260,"uid":275903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T02:30:38.000Z","msg":"雪雪聲"},{"pid":"999caa970f4ff45c08ffe67ca315e4b97ab63916","tid":2014260,"uid":117301,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"repl